videos.headline: Eric Williams powers down fast-break slam for Oregon
videos.description: Oregon's Eric Williams Jr. comes up with the steal and races down the court to cram down a two-handed flush on the break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Eric Williams powers down fast-break slam for Oregon) 2022/01/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon's Eric Williams cashes out step-back buzzer-beater at half
videos.description: Eric Williams Jr. uses a step-back to create space then splashes a deep 3-pinter to beat the halftime buzzer and give Oregon a 45-29 lead over USC.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Oregon's Eric Williams cashes out step-back buzzer-beater at half) 2022/01/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon's N'Faly Dante throws down rim-rattling slam
videos.description: N'Faly Dante gets the pass on the fast break and leaves the rim shaking after he throws down a powerful slam for Oregon.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Oregon's N'Faly Dante throws down rim-rattling slam) 2022/01/16 ESHEET
